description.narrative: UNICEF works closely with the MSWRR by coordinating technical support in drafting of the Rules and facilitating multisectoral thematic consultations to ensure that they are feasible and implementable. The Draft 1 of the Rules has been submitted to the government for approval. Significant work has been done in the area of social workforce strengthening and improvement of the national case management system - focusing more on the quality of services. The process of developing the national Child Protection Policy was officially launched and the work on development of the Policy continues. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:30/07/2020
